underlying_goal: Reduce the length of a research paper to meet page limits by moving figures and cutting text.
primary_success: Providing a detailed, prioritized list of seven potential text cuts to help the user meet their page count goal.
brief_summary: The user needed to shorten a paper. Claude moved figures to the appendix as requested, then provided a prioritized list of seven text cuts. The user and Claude iteratively worked through the list, applying the edits to reduce the paper's length.
